README.md

Awesome Unity

   [https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome]Awesome

   A categorized community-driven collection of high-quality awesome Unity
   assets, projects, and resources. Free assets and resources are
   prioritized over paid when possible.

   Suggestions and contributions are always welcome! Make sure to read the
   [https://github.com/RyanNielson/awesome-unity/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.
   md]contribution guidelines for more information before submitting a
   pull request.

   Thanks to all the
   [https://github.com/ryannielson/awesome-unity/graphs/contributors]contr
   ibutors, this wouldn't be possible without you!
     * Awesome Unity
          + 2D
          + AI
          + Augmented & Virtual Reality
          + Camera
          + Character Controllers
          + Frameworks
          + Input
          + Modeling
          + Monetization
          + Networking
          + Scripting
          + Services
          + Shaders
          + Tweening
          + UI
          + Utilities
          + Visual Scripting
